{"tid":1127193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天氣預報：局部地區狂風雷暴　稍後驟雨較多","createTime":"2019-04-27T02:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T02:59:55.000Z","uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"54b6b3661ce1c955273cee33f83b735f55a5f672","tid":1127193,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:33:41.000Z","msg":"一股達強風程度的偏東氣流正影響廣東沿岸地區，同時高空擾動正為華南沿岸帶來雷雨。天文台在今早(27日)8時錄得氣溫25度，相對濕度81%，過去一小時京士柏錄得的平均紫外線指數是0.2，強度屬於低。 <br />\n<br />\n預測大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨，局部地區有狂風雷暴，稍後驟雨較多，最高氣溫約27度。吹和緩至清勁東風，離岸間中吹強風；展望明日(28日)仍有驟雨，隨後一兩日部分時間有陽光及炎熱。"},{"pid":"b9d7d1bed2c5e7fd4b40c870a55c6d21be0ee06d","tid":1127193,"uid":52605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:35:39.000Z","msg":"連個天都同天文台作對"},{"pid":"038b6a90b3ae5047e9149b08528b38cc5cff9e8e","tid":1127193,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"信其他地區天文臺都唔信香港大交合"},{"pid":"720caf589dcbe39872d86c9f1890ecae72a9f683","tid":1127193,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"其實天文台pattern好準<br />\n只係遲幾日姐"},{"pid":"a9d9683e01e8cc3277601cff3c77e470f620d27d","tid":1127193,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"香港天文台執撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"a23bb78acd7a378793c16de0d3f20b8646a6f149","tid":1127193,"uid":109462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"720caf589dcbe39872d86c9f1890ecae72a9f683","tid":1127193,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"其實天文台pattern好準<br />\n只係遲幾日姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:52:46.000Z","msg":"氣象界沈大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3aa9e39997f94b558a41a29174b8317e5970e4b","tid":1127193,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"自己去睇雷達圖，今日有d料<br />\n<br />\n細尺度的雷雨區好難準確計算二十四小時會唔會入去香港市區"},{"pid":"16fc43e2d6a8ca3e